public <T> T evaluate(Exchange exchange, Class<T> type) {     Object value = evaluate(exchange).     if (Object.class == type) {         // do not use type converter if type is Object (optimize)         return (T) value.     }     return exchange.getContext().getTypeConverter().convertTo(type, exchange, value). }
